snippet.title: Bloody Hell - OUT NOW (Launch trailer)
snippet.description:
The past 5 months I've been making my first ever Steam game. It will release on January 27th for free!

Interested in trying it out? Play it now on Steam! - 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2056220/Bloody_Hell/ 
You can also join our Discord!
https://discord.gg/xE2K6x5TWu

Bloody Hell is a short but sweet game about an Angel on a Bloody Bullet-hell mission to kill Satan! Dash, Double Dash, Grapple & Blast your way through Hell to fulfill your Holy Mission. Will you be able to kill Satan? Or will you fail to master your abilities and DIE in this BLO ODY HELL?
